                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>&quot;Remember me&quot; implored the Thief!</l>
                    <l>Oh Hospitality!  </l>
                    <l>My Guest &quot;Today in Paradise&quot; </l>
                    <l>I give thee<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 guaranty.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>That Courtesy<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 will fair remain</l>
                    <l>When the Delight<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 is Dust </l>
                    <l>With which we<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 cite this mightiest<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 case </l>
                    <l>Of compensated<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 trust.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Of all we are<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 allowed to hope<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>But Affidavit<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 stands</l>
                    <l>That this was<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 due where most<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 we fear </l>
                    <l>Be unexpected<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Friends.  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
